'''Theodore Nisbet Gibbs''' (3 February 1896&ndash;15 July 1978) was a New Zealand law clerk, accountant, businessman and tax adviser. He was born in [[Whangaroa]], [[Northland Region|Northland]], [[New Zealand]] on 3 February 1896.<ref name="DNZB Gibbs">{{DNZB|title=Theodore Nisbet Gibbs|first= Peter J.|last= Lineham|id=5g7|accessdate=23 April 2017}}</ref>

